 134:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\drivers/peripheral/syspm/cy_syspm.h **** *
 135:Generated_Source\PSoC6\pdl\drivers/peripheral/syspm/cy_syspm.h **** *   - The total current consumption must be less than or equal to 
